g.text: STEP 1: run query Q1 on base table, let's call the
result R1, R1 goes to result table.
STEP 2: apply the recursive step (query Q2) on
R1, append the result (R2) in the result table.
STEP 3: apply the recursive step (query Q2) on R2,
append the result (R3) in the result table.
STEP N: apply the recursive step (query Q2) on RN-1,
append the result (RN) in the result table, continue
Finally, select desired records from result table.
